Official Reference:

This repository contains the official reference ontology maintained by the CBD
Secretariat. While you are free to use and adapt this ontology under the CC-BY
4.0 IGO license, only versions published by the CBD Secretariat at
http://metadata.cbd.int/kmgbf/ontology are considered official reference versions.

Derivative works must clearly indicate they are adaptations and not official CBD
versions.

